<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1112057-how-bad-is-the-killing-of-animals-in-the">How bad is the killing of animals in the book? I&#39;m always disturbed by killing people, but as an animal lover I get a deep sadness that stays with me when innocent animals are killed.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1112057'><a id="like_count_community_question_1112057" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1112057?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">10 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F33155777-fierce-kingdom">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
